moji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我諗香港都冇咁易撞鬼啩，咁多人，問下屋企人有冇執啲咩騎呢野番屋企，冇就我諗唔會關鬼事，可能小朋友貪玩，可能係屋企人頂對門果陣整出嚟姐"},{"pid":"e93d11fa5db097b6b7e6da87a465f0a727eed8e8","tid":177024,"uid":34852,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-28T14:55:18.000Z","msg":"用marker圈住佢<br />\n提一提個賊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ef864f900821955e2f15ef394d6ad377e4cc6d34","tid":177024,"uid":53126,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-28T15:16:56.000Z","msg":"不如影埋鐵閘向門果面睇下係咪鐵閘撞成咁<br />\n不過睇返D痕跡，似係比長遮督/鐵錘打過咁喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a42442ed3c2e9fc367558ee1e02b4b06d49cbf0c","tid":177024,"uid":17538,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-28T15:30:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>不如影埋鐵閘向門果面睇下係咪鐵閘撞成咁<br />\n不過睇返D痕跡，似係比長遮督/鐵錘打過咁喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n出左去 晏小小<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1f5afa045172f90b5bca6e83b1150f0a6671a6df","tid":177024,"uid":17538,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-28T15:30:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>搵張白紙遮住佢，驚既話寫埋&rdquo;呢到冇暗號&ldquo;</blockquote><br />\n驚撞鬼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我諗香港都冇咁易撞鬼啩，咁多人，問下屋企人有冇執啲咩騎呢野番屋企，冇就我諗唔會關鬼事，可能小朋友貪玩，可能係屋企人頂對門果陣整出嚟姐</blockquote><br />\n應該唔會係對面<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9e1ce220a89fb4514604c262ea2238dc2f4edc99","tid":177024,"uid":29080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-28T15:30:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e99468c4ed4ca68c625b1157bbfffe5d678491af","tid":177024,"uid":36702,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-28T15:56:17.000Z","msg":"請十個毒撚去你屋企衝陽氣"},{"pid":"9913b33cdd7d5b26708aeecd196d325fabb40b94","tid":177024,"uid":17538,"like"